      "type": "text",
      "data": "<font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">arch 显示机器的处理器架构(1)&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">uname -m 显示机器的处理器架构(2)&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">uname -r 显示正在使用的内核版本&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">dmidecode -q 显示硬件系统部件 - (SMBIOS / DMI)&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">hdparm -i /dev/hda 罗列一个磁盘的架构特性&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">hdparm -tT /dev/sda 在磁盘上执行测试性读取操作&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cat /proc/cpuinfo 显示CPU info的信息&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cat /proc/interrupts 显示中断&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cat /proc/meminfo 校验内存使用&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cat /proc/swaps 显示哪些swap被使用&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cat /proc/version 显示内核的版本&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cat /proc/net/dev 显示网络适配器及统计&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cat /proc/mounts 显示已加载的文件系统&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">lspci -tv 罗列 PCI 设备&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">lsusb -tv 显示 USB 设备&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">date 显示系统日期&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">cal 2007 显示2007年的日历表&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">date 041217002007.00 设置日期和时间 - 月日时分年.秒&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;\">clock -w 将时间修改保存到 BIOS&nbsp;</span></font>"
    }
  ]
